<br>
I'm 99% sure that the shovel does NOT influence the level of the pet summoned though. The Staves will increase the raw level of a pet. The SolRo focus items will increase some of the supporting stats. <br>
<br>
When I use a 49 earth pet summoned with a shovel, it only hits for a max of 54, which tells me it is one level less than max (which is what they did with all of the 49+ pets to allow for the staves to function.)<br>
<br>
from the compendium:<br>
